  # Delete Knowledge
  Remove um knowledgement pelo ID (remove do banco; objeto no S3 permanece).
  Required role: ORGANIZATION
  Substitua `REPLACE_WITH_KNOWLEDGE_UUID` pelo UUID obtido no List Knowledge.
}
